{"id":"godeploy-api-icg","title":"Implement payment processing for subscriptions","description":"When users start trialing the Unlimited plan, implement actual payment collection. Decision made during pricing page buildout - using 14-day trial to buy time before needing real payments.\n\n## Context\n- Pricing page now allows users to select plans and start 14-day trials\n- Trial status is shown on pricing page (Trial ends in X days)\n- Downgrade flow warns users they'll lose features and can't re-trial\n\n## Implementation Plan\n1. Integrate Stripe for payment processing\n2. Add payment form/Stripe Elements to collect card details\n3. Store Stripe customer ID and payment method\n4. Handle trial-to-paid conversion (charge when trial ends)\n5. Handle failed payments and subscription cancellation\n6. Add billing history/invoices page\n7. Implement subscription webhooks from Stripe\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Stripe integration set up (API keys, webhooks)\n- [ ] Payment details collected before or during trial\n- [ ] Automatic charging when trial ends\n- [ ] Failed payment handling with grace period\n- [ ] Users can update payment method\n- [ ] Billing history viewable in dashboard","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-12-04T10:13:07.702813101-05:00","updated_at":"2025-12-04T10:13:07.702813101-05:00","labels":["payments","stripe","subscriptions"]}
